text: Ignace Iamak (born 23 March 1990) is a Vanuatuan footballer who plays as a defender for Nalkutan in the Port Vila Football League. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Vanuatuan footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Vanuatu international footballers Category:Tafea F.C. players
